{"tid":2005453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(震驚14億人) 調查指中国人最滿意政府抗疫表現　日本人最不滿","createTime":"2020-05-07T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T07:02:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd02e87d2b31308fe474053e37a317996807194","tid":2005453,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"一項在周三（6日）公布結果的調查發現，中國的民眾大多滿意政府應對新冠肺炎疫情的表現，但西方國家的國民則認為自己的政府表現差勁，對自身政府抗疫評價最低的是日本人。<br />\n<br />\n有關研究由新加坡民調機構Blackbox Research與科技公司Toluna合作進行，訪問了全球23個國家及地區的民眾，了解他們對自己政府應付新冠肺炎疫情的看法，採用的4個指標包括政治領導、企業領導、社會和傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n調查結果顯示中國的得分最高，有85分，大部分受訪者在4項指標中，都給予政府正面評價。排名第2的越南有77分，隨後是同為取得59分的阿聯酋和印度；而得56分的新西蘭，是唯一分數高於全球平均分（45分）的西方國家。調查指出，這表示西方國家的人民普遍不滿政府應對疫情的表現。 <br />\n<br />\n 美國、澳洲、意大利、德國、英國和法國的得分，都比全球平均分數低，其中法國只有26分，全球排名尾二；全球最低分的國家是日本，只獲得16分。<br />\n<br />\nBlackbox Research創始人兼行政總裁布萊克（David Black）指出，總括來說大部分國家及地區的抗疫表現都不符人民的期望，而中國人例外地滿意政府表現的原因，可能是當全球疫情大爆發之際，中國已經踏入康復期，令人覺得中國政府把疫情處理得好。 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200507/bkn-20200507030039760-0507_00912_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6a11b810b2574bf752288d5589e01230248bee69","tid":2005453,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"想問<br />\n中国人幾時有唔滿意過政府表現"},{"pid":"1268cd2f3df18dd5837b8250b3edd169687d3c39","tid":2005453,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a11b810b2574bf752288d5589e01230248bee69","tid":2005453,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"想問<br />\n中国人幾時有唔滿意過政府表現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"有，不滿冇得永續習近平，跪係到求習總修改憲法"},{"pid":"c4e771ebafd6b62ab70a252335a604954ba379d5","tid":2005453,"uid":41116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8sGrnDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8sGrnDS.png&h=c2ded1ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e302c36807a4bef646b59cf1cb613235c930e2c6","tid":2005453,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"中共果套全民監控體制，處理疫情係完美工具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家西方都開始學緊支共果套，我懷疑人類以後會冇晒私隱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe54055e4c714f799cbe9d828eb4e68bb83e42c3","tid":2005453,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個夠膽話唔滿意？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沒有、沒有、沒有&hellip; 通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f34c2e39f4e606821d83e7a56b20fd9cad74931","tid":2005453,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe54055e4c714f799cbe9d828eb4e68bb83e42c3","tid":2005453,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個夠膽話唔滿意？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沒有、沒有、沒有&hellip; 通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"但佢地依家真心覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12461c9e4eb9a0adca548b99428ea3275fb3249","tid":2005453,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f34c2e39f4e606821d83e7a56b20fd9cad74931","tid":2005453,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe54055e4c714f799cbe9d828eb4e68bb83e42c3","tid":2005453,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"<spa